   114ã
   115ã/* ==========================================================================
   116ã   TOKENS LAYER
   117ã   Design tokens as CSS custom properties on :root.
   118ã
   119ã   Token system:
   120ã   - Spacing:    4px base unit, named --space-xs through --space-3xl
   121ã   - Colors:     oklch color space for perceptual uniformity
   122ã   - Typography: System font stack, fluid type scale with clamp()
